Package: MeanRarity
Type: Package
Title: Estimates Diversity Using The Mean Rarity Framework
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2020-07-01
Maintainer: Michael Roswell <mroswell.rutgers@gmail.comt>
Description: This package contains functions to estimate [Hill] diversity as a function of a scaling parameter \eqn{\ell}, as well as various convenience functions for sampling communities, estimating diversity from subsamples, and computing uncertainty estimates. 
